      <div style="width:400px;float:left;">
        <p style="color:#888; line-height:2em; font-size:13px"><b>Social Data Discovery</b> is a solution for public and private institutions that need to transform raw data, contained in large departmental databases, into "finished good" datasets that can be easily consumed by an online community.</p>

        <p style="color:#888; line-height:2em; font-size:13px">Using the latest Web 2.0 technologies, Social Data Discovery promotes civic engagement, enabling an online community of journalists, policy makers, scientists/domain experts, and citizens to visualize data and engage in discussion with one another.  Together, audiences with disparate viewpoints can analyze and discover insights from datasets, improving decision and policy making.  Social Data Discovery:</p>
